| Parameter | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `"`***text***`"` | yes | The text to render. Supports inline markup (§[4.5](#45-strings)). |
| `left` \| `center` \| `right` | no | Horizontal alignment around the anchor point. Default `left`. |
